beer.beer_description:
A true milkshake with massive additions of succulent strawberries, silky lactose, and rich vanilla. Sabro and home-grown Enigma Hops add just the right slice of hoppiness without the distraction from the chewy hits of ripe strawberry and luscious vanilla.

All built on a brilliant base of oats, wheat and a sensational Nitro serve.
